        " «أَجْزَأَهُ."
      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.bab-ul-qaim-publications": [
          "Hadith.1000 - Ahmad ibn Muhammad ibn Abi Nasr al-Bazanti asked Imam al-Ridha (as) about a man who forgot to say the Takbir al-Ihram (opening Takbir) until he had already said the Takbir for bowing (ruku').\nImam (as) replied: \"It suffices him”."
        ]
